俾佢地？係都醫護啦"},{"pid":"853df8bee18f882d357a4dd21c5b9d0a30496624","tid":1874404,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05ac897721b3cea08c945bec0629c7d5e0fdc6ec","tid":1874404,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"其實唔係好明，既然廢老藍絲係敵人<br />\n點解仲要大愛撚上身<br />\n抱住救人先既道德觀念<br />\n<br />\n求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ea0b337cb02ec2d579ce82cdfb795e075717c2","tid":1874404,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"黃絲捐錢蝕賣比藍絲"},{"pid":"fcbb4bd65389b5915db4c32311939c3d7ee32286","tid":1874404,"uid":201374,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"247cddfcacd8e12f167154184fe10c367f315de4","tid":1874404,"uid":47222,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:43:59.000Z","msg":"唔好又優先派比廢老阿 班友明明唔出街都得 <br />\n要比醫護同低收入真香港人先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"仲俾醫護！？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n次次出嚟屌嗰班偽善左膠買裝俾醫護入境，就有一大班道德高地撚衝出嚟護航<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味，提供保護裝備係顧主嘅責任，唔係市民<br />\n照足安全指引，口罩一除就掉，要裝就問顧主拎，冇就唔出房唔開工<br />\n完全合法合情合理，要嘈自己去同勞工處嘈<br />\n冇裝俾顧員就自己揾林鄭自己揾狗<br />\n<br />\n成班智障仲買口罩俾醫護俾入境拎光環自我感覺良好<br />\n帶私貨嘢俾錢返工<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老味原來送晒啲防護用品俾支那，班黃絲就會幫你買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係港共我就全撚部送晒上去領功喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n橫掂唔俾裝你你都會自己搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"03ec22ca77b17e0c054c5d02ec2f6b89224244b8","tid":1874404,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04cda64efb1f8636af60e8cf65b6455bc7bab2f9","tid":1874404,"uid":325869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9950282060b9d97ac302a57b35e1c5555f703735","tid":1874404,"uid":289978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"優先賣俾學生先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"學生唔駛返學、唔駛開工，又精壯，點解要賣俾佢地？係都醫護啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔係學生先?政權諸多打壓學生，抽起大學生褔利，攻打大學殺絕知識份子，依家就係要用黃色經濟圈去建立年青人社會。<br />\n<br />\n俾醫護先?藍絲蝗護死全家。"},{"pid":"c0f507efa06b30bb2994e2a59adf98494d6f28c0","tid":1874404,"uid":201374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04cda64efb1f8636af60e8cf65b6455bc7bab2f9","tid":1874404,"uid":325869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9950282060b9d97ac302a57b35e1c5555f703735","tid":1874404,"uid":289978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"優先賣俾學生先"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:47:45.000Z","msg":"學生唔駛返學、唔駛開工，又精壯，點解要賣俾佢地？係都醫護啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:57:11.000Z","msg":"收皮啦垃圾左膠<br />\n醫護要裝係應該去揾佢嘅顧主啊on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n顧主提供唔到，唔係零裝做嘢，唔係自購裝備做嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪撚做嘢啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ea5141dea6eb40b99cbe827b8a0264b9f5fb1e8","tid":1874404,"uid":201374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05ac897721b3cea08c945bec0629c7d5e0fdc6ec","tid":1874404,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:50:00.000Z","msg":"其實唔係好明，既然廢老藍絲係敵人<br />\n點解仲要大愛撚上身<br />\n抱住救人先既道德觀念<br />\n<br />\n求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:58:53.000Z","msg":"因為大愛左膠又上晒身<br />\n同私了嘅時候拉住手足叫「唔好打喇打死人喇」嘅人一撚樣<br />\n香港咁撚多鍾意企道德高地嘅左膠，真係冇撚得救"},{"pid":"ba36e142e3b4ab152b55318b7f65b698b1f7bda5","tid":1874404,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9950282060b9d97ac302a57b35e1c5555f703735","tid":1874404,"uid":289978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"優先賣俾學生先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"